A '''brothel guard''' is a character in the [[Season 5|fifth season]]. He will be played by [[Mishael Lopes Cardozo]].<ref>[http://watchersonthewall.com/mishael-lopes-cardozo-cast-game-thrones-season-5]</ref> He will meet [[Varys]] and [[Tyrion Lannister]].
